{"tid":2036980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【第卅玖期牆紙】 這個璀璨都市光輝到此？","createTime":"2020-05-26T18:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T02:00:19.000Z","uid":253119,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"765836760c10c650582b12c1f2340a624b9cf595","tid":2036980,"uid":253119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:59:55.000Z","msg":"由北方而來的暴風雨侵襲這城。<br />\n兩星期來政權步步進迫，首位以暴動罪入獄的義士判囚四年、考評局的「民族感情」風波、《頭條新聞》暫停製作、到人大越權立《國安法》。燈塔一座又一座熄滅，不禁令人反問，這個璀璨都市是否光輝到此？<br />\n<br />\n有人把希望寄於城外，於風雨中堅定飛航；有人作了長久對抗的預備，年復年地把集體意識根植於這土地；有人願點燃身軀，用火光驅趕黑暗照亮街道。在黎明之前，仍有牆紙陪伴大家。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n目錄<br />\n1. 中國殖民香港：抗殖之道<br />\n2. 金錢洗腦<br />\n3. Ideas are Bulletproof. Ideas are our Bullets.<br />\n4. 在再次勇武之前<br />\n5. 國際戰線使用手冊<br />\n6. 抗爭老師的自白<br />\n7. 周梓樂被香港警察謀殺身亡，半年<br />\n8. Post-1984<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n點擊連結用投稿衝擊牆紙：@wallpaperneedyou<br />\n<br />\n#39期 #39th<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5hKSF0X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5hKSF0X.jpg&h=b5c060af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6dcF0Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6dcF0Y.jpg&h=6ee14a61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mwQRWzj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmwQRWzj.jpg&h=517c2bf9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AH3oNF0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAH3oNF0.jpg&h=662b7870&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P8gYBzn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP8gYBzn.jpg&h=4a550b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkDDBzp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkDDBzp.jpg&h=adcf7b8